Package: lpt
Type: Package
Title: Local Parallel Trends for Continuous Difference-in-Differences
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Francesco", "Dealberti", email = "dealberti.francesco@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements partial identification under Local Parallel Trends (LPT)
    for continuous difference-in-differences designs. Bounds the selection slope
    mu'(d) by a sensitivity parameter B (a Lipschitz bound), yielding identified
    sets for the dose-response derivative and ATT level effects. Estimation uses
    penalized regression splines via mgcv. See Dealberti (2026) for details.
